26#ifndef _INTEL_RENDERSTATE_H
27#define _INTEL_RENDERSTATE_H
28
29#include "i915_drv.h"
30
31extern const struct intel_renderstate_rodata gen6_null_state;
32extern const struct intel_renderstate_rodata gen7_null_state;
33extern const struct intel_renderstate_rodata gen8_null_state;
34extern const struct intel_renderstate_rodata gen9_null_state;
35
36#define RO_RENDERSTATE(_g) \
37 const struct intel_renderstate_rodata gen ## _g ## _null_state = { \
38 .reloc = gen ## _g ## _null_state_relocs, \
39 .batch = gen ## _g ## _null_state_batch, \
40 .batch_items = sizeof(gen ## _g ## _null_state_batch)/4, \
41 }
42
43#endif /* INTEL_RENDERSTATE_H */
